            <sentence>
                <offset>0</offset>
                <text>Patient 4 was diagnosed with CHH at 4 months.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>46</offset>
                <text>She had short stature with short limbs, sparse hair, joint hypermobility and varus deformity.</text>
                <annotation id="1">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0004322</infon>
                    <location length="13" offset="8"/>
                    <text>short stature</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="2">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0009826</infon>
                    <location length="11" offset="27"/>
                    <text>short limbs</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="3">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0008070</infon>
                    <location length="11" offset="40"/>
                    <text>sparse hair</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="4">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0001382</infon>
                    <location length="19" offset="53"/>
                    <text>joint hypermobility</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="5">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="Comment">! Unclear phenotype</infon>
                    <location length="15" offset="77"/>
                    <text>varus deformity</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>140</offset>
                <text>Her growth followed the −5.0 SDS curve.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>180</offset>
                <text>At 2 years, she presented with severe anemia (Hb 45 g/L) and almost total erythroaplasia on bone marrow evaluation.</text>
                <annotation id="6">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0001903</infon>
                    <location length="6" offset="38"/>
                    <text>anemia</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="7">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <location length="14" offset="74"/>
                    <text>erythroaplasia</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>296</offset>
                <text>Anemia recovered spontaneously and the etiology remained unknown.</text>
                <annotation id="8">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0001903</infon>
                    <location length="6" offset="0"/>
                    <text>Anemia</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>362</offset>
                <text>At 6.5 years, she developed aggressive B-cell lymphoma.</text>
                <annotation id="9">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0012191</infon>
                    <location length="15" offset="39"/>
                    <text>B-cell lymphoma</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>418</offset>
                <text>Primary tumor was detected in the adrenal gland and pulmonary metastases were present at diagnosis.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>518</offset>
                <text>Treatment was unsuccessful and she died at the age of 7 years.</text>
            </sentence>
        </passage>
    </document>
